# ATLAS Utils Directory

This directory contains utility functions and helpers for ATLAS features.

Utils to be implemented:
- atlas-error-mapper.ts - Maps API error responses to user-friendly messages
- atlas-retry-strategy.ts - Implements retry logic with exponential backoff
- atlas-validators.ts - Custom form validators for ATLAS data
- atlas-date-utils.ts - Date formatting and manipulation utilities
- atlas-state-utils.ts - State transition validation helpers
- atlas-export-utils.ts - Data export formatting utilities

Utilities provide reusable functionality across ATLAS components and services.
